        <h2>Chinese Painting General Info<a name="cp1"></a></h2>
        <p>
            <strong><a name="cp2"></a>Painting Dimensions</strong><br>
            Dimensions listed are for the size of the painted material.
            Example: all 	Shikishi paintings are approximately
